* aCmsPage

  Add a real cms page object to generate route

      a_page:
          url:      /:sf_culture/:slug
          class:    aCmsRoute
          options:  { model: aPage, type: object }
          param:    { module: a, action: show }
          requirements:
            sf_method:  [post, get, head]
            sf_culture: (fr|en)
            slug: .*